        Parameters:
        currency - Currency code of the tax
        amount - Amount of the tax
        code - The tax code which identifies the tax. Examples: 1=BED_TAX 2=CITY_TAX
        percentage - percentage of the tax. Use together with pricingFrequency and pricingMode
        included - Is the tax included in the base amount
        description - Textual description of the tax
        pricingFrequency - Specifies if the tax applies per stay or per night - PER_STAY - PER_NIGHT
        pricingMode - Specifies if the tax applies per occupant or per room - PER_OCCUPANT - PER_PRODUCT
